Last night in Emain, a level 34 minstrel that joined our group, had a level 48 gorbachend as a pet.  During the 45 mins or so that he was with us, he never once lost control of that pet.  He used speed song, he stunned, and he used the pet to kill.  There is just something fundamentally wrong with that.  I'm a level 46 Sorceress and the pet was orange to me.  It was purple to the Minstrel.<P>And what do Sorcs have?  Oh, yeah...tenacity.<P>--------------------<P>Badea<BR>Sorceress Bedevere
