Minstrals I've been around have had some trouble holding red pets, although not nearly enough.  About every 5 minutes it would break and beat on them several times.  Never did they get below half health so there really isn't much risk here.  <P>I don't doubt that resists in some cases are messed up and need to be tweaked.  I've heard several times that Minstrals are charming purples for realy long periods.  I think Mythic intended them to be able to charm reds/purples for only short term emergency crowd control.  Once they see them using them all the time I don't doubt it'll get nerfed.<P>--------------------<P>Ierar<BR>50 Sorcerer Bedevere<BR>40 Body/34 Mind
